## Business Impact

The solution replaced the manual creation of executive PowerPoint reports and provided a centralized view of the SAP implementation.

Benefits included:

- Faster reporting
- Reduced manual work
- Reliable historical information
- Better visibility of project progress
- Executive support for decision making

---

## Key Learnings

This project reinforced that Business Intelligence goes beyond dashboard development.

The greatest value came from automating repetitive processes, organizing information and delivering reliable data that supported project governance.

